# Architecture Rules

## Responsibility

Translate Specifications into system design. Protect long-term changeability.

## Required artifacts

- Architecture doc in `docs/04_Architecture/` for non-trivial systems
- ADR in `docs/05_ADR/` for significant / hard-to-reverse decisions

## Allowed outputs

- Boundaries, flows, trust models, failure modes
- Alternatives considered with trade-offs
- Guardrails for implementers

## Forbidden

- Silent tech selection in chat without writing ADR/Architecture
- Designing features that are not specified
- Premature microservice explosion
- Putting secrets in docs or infra files

## Traceability

Architecture must cite Spec IDs it realizes.
